high_descs: Move left then left again heading to the round black table
Pick up the black mug with the spoon on top of the table
Carry the mug and spoon over to the counter directly above the dishwasher
Place the black mug and spoon on top of the counter
anns.task_desc: Move a black mug and spoon to the counter top

high_descs: Turn right, pass the stove, turn right at the sink, and continue straight until you get to the round black table.
Pick up the black cup and spoon from the table.
Turn around and carry the cup and spoon to stand at the counter in front of the dishwasher.
Place the cup and spoon on the counter directly in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Move a cup and spoon to the counter by the toaster.

high_descs: Turn right, walk over to the kitchen sink, make another right and walk up to the black table.
Pick up the spoon and black mug that is on the table.
Turn around and walk forward a few steps before turning right to face the toaster.
Place the mug and spoon down on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Move a mug and spoon from the table to the counter.
